scenes.description: The members of holoX are playing a giant tilting maze game called 'Giant Seesaw'. They struggle with the physics and inertia of the game as they try to guide balls into goals.
After the first round, the members catch their breath, discuss their score (51), and prepare for a second attempt with a new strategy.
The second round begins. The group is much more focused, discovering a '99' bonus ball that leads to high intensity and shouting as they navigate the maze.
